snippet.title: Comic Con News
snippet.description: Comic Con News cover events around London and in United Kingdom. Some of the Comic cons We have covered MCM London Comic Con, MCM Birmingham, London Film and Comic Con, St albans Comic Con, CosXpo, EGX Rezzed etc... We do interviews with guests, cosplay music videos, news and highlights and walkthroughs. Subscribe to get the latest news.
